commit message:
Update README.md

Just a small clarification to get busybox to work. This might help n00bs like me :-)
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/danielmmmm/oandbackup into danielmmmm-master

Smarter regex for finding users

Will also eliminate the use of awk which doesn't seem to be supported by
toybox yet.

Remove old code for unpacking tar archives

Tar archives have been deprecated since
677b0068ea5220a10745d9de5271296ab38f4038

Repopulate appInfoList if it is null

This can happen when returning to the batch activity after a long time.
Don't refer to the full name of Build every time
Set default *box according to api level

Indicate disabled packages with a different colour

As requested in issue 126
https://github.com/jensstein/oandbackup/issues/126
